<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0090a" xml:id="I01.0036.0090a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0090a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 36</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0090a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>安村道俗一百餘人修塔記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0090a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0090a0101">夫脩心始行。必資願表。表願功能。道由生養。生養之功。謂之塔像。故八塔顯自碧林。
<lb ed="I" n="0090a02" type="honorific"/>影髮著之香樹。是使見形立善。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090001" n="0090001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090001" n="0090001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090001" n="0090001"/>範<anchor xml:id="end0090001"/>像流今。若非曠積<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090002" n="0090002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090002" n="0090002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090002" n="0090002"/>深<anchor xml:id="end0090002"/>因。慈悲宿造。則必弱<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090003" n="0090003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090003" n="0090003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090003" n="0090003"/>喪<anchor xml:id="end0090003"/>忘歸。
<lb ed="I" n="0090a03" type="honorific"/>長迷誰覺。唯雅見君子能改<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090004" n="0090004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090004" n="0090004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090004" n="0090004"/>步<anchor xml:id="end0090004"/>迷方。控平軒於一乘。移心弱<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>喪<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>。汎神舟於三路。是以
<lb ed="I" n="0090a04" type="honorific"/>獲<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090005" n="0090005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090005" n="0090005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090005" n="0090005"/>嘉<anchor xml:id="end0090005"/>縣東。清流福地。號曰安村。有大檀主。　　　置立尼寺。有故天宮一區。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090006" n="0090006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090006" n="0090006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090006" n="0090006"/>年<anchor xml:id="end0090006"/>久事
<lb ed="I" n="0090a05" type="honorific"/>遐。神功頓毀。寶色莊嚴。散靈像於輕塵。陵雲雅<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090007" n="0090007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090007" n="0090007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090007" n="0090007"/>製<anchor xml:id="end0090007"/>。落真儀於重壤。玉地<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="star"/>深<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>經。髣髴若
<lb ed="I" n="0090a06" type="honorific"/>存。寶相祇林。神容中斷。乃復道俗一百餘人。發悟自心。輕財重道。捨身命財。共脩故
<lb ed="I" n="0090a07" type="honorific"/>塔。始末十旬。微功乃就。復妙相於靈山。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090008" n="0090008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090008" n="0090008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090008" n="0090008"/>還<anchor xml:id="end0090008"/>湛一於雙樹。義感去來。精貫<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">現</unclear>在。邈<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090009" n="0090009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090009" n="0090009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090009" n="0090009"/>象<anchor xml:id="end0090009"/>護
<lb ed="I" n="0090a08" type="honorific"/>於金經。超名敕於玉牒。釋梵來儀。乘碧霧以通煙。四王效像。曜五花於日月。淨水香
<lb ed="I" n="0090a09" type="honorific"/>雲。若<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0090010" n="0090010"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0090010" n="0090010"/><anchor xml:id="beg0090010" n="0090010"/>離<anchor xml:id="end0090010"/>復合。異物芬芳。殊方恒在。金剛豈遠。此地長春。十種莊嚴。事同紫岸。因茲業
<lb ed="I" n="0090a10" type="honorific"/>也。一百人等。發斯洪願。願令　皇家。寶運<anchor xml:id="beg_3" type="star"/>深<anchor xml:id="end_3"/>基。道契二儀之堅。玉蒂金根。福同九山
<lb ed="I" n="0090a11" type="honorific"/>之宅。異物諍祥。雲華帝門。奇<g ref="#CB30664">󷟈</g>競像。風翻上國。破四魔於五雲。拔三鋒於四濘。甘露
<lb ed="I" n="0090a12" type="honorific"/>淨音。導一乘於方方。法水金開。灌千迷於莫二。三有一歸。同軒佛寶。哀鸞和雅。調八
<lb ed="I" n="0090a13" type="honorific"/>梵於清蓮。冥讚空絃。妙龍舟於幽俗。往聖所以懸苻。來賢所以共一。思報四恩。常脩
<lb ed="I" n="0090a14" type="honorific"/>□度。火劍自消。三途永息。莫不盡化<anchor xml:id="beg_4" type="star"/>還<anchor xml:id="end_4"/>无。妙鄰二智。滅諦夷然。誰非佛者。奉慈氏於
<lb ed="I" n="0090a15" type="honorific"/>初覺。會千佛於淨<anchor xml:id="beg_5" type="star"/>年<anchor xml:id="end_5"/>。正心正見。唯願如是。
<lb ed="I" n="0090a16" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　　唯大魏天平四<anchor xml:id="beg_6" type="star"/>年<anchor xml:id="end_6"/>歲次丁巳七月甲午朔廿五日戊午</p>
</cb:div>
